702151f-a.title: Bronx: White Plains Road - Gunhill Road (East)
702151f-a.text:
White Plains Road, adjoining to the south East Gunhill Road,
showing a public comfort station under construction by the W.P.A.
The building stands in a little public square which divides the
thoroughfare in two separate lanes.
December 14, 1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Art Project photo.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
